body:
# Issue Management

Issues are GitHub's built-in task tracker. Every bug report, feature request, and work item lives as an issue inside a repository. The API provides full control over issue creation, search, labeling, assignment, and lifecycle management.

## Creating an Issue

```javascript
import { Octokit } from "@octokit/rest";

const octokit = new Octokit({ auth: process.env.GITHUB_TOKEN });

const { data: issue } = await octokit.issues.create({
  owner: "my-org",
  repo: "my-project",
  title: "Bug: login fails on Safari",
  body: "## Steps to reproduce\n1. Open Safari\n2. Navigate to /login\n3. Enter credentials\n\n## Expected\nRedirect to dashboard\n\n## Actual\n500 error page",
  labels: ["bug", "priority:high"],
  assignees: ["developer-1"],
  milestone: 3,
});
console.log(issue.number, issue.html_url);
```

## Searching Issues

```javascript
// Search with GitHub query syntax
const { data: results } = await octokit.search.issuesAndPullRequests({
  q: "repo:my-org/my-project is:issue is:open label:bug sort:created-desc",
  per_page: 20,
});

// List issues for a repo
const { data: issues } = await octokit.issues.listForRepo({
  owner: "my-org",
  repo: "my-project",
  state: "open",
  labels: "bug,priority:high",
  sort: "created",
  direction: "desc",
});
```

## Managing Labels

```javascript
// Create a label
await octokit.issues.createLabel({
  owner: "my-org",
  repo: "my-project",
  name: "priority:critical",
  color: "d73a4a",
  description: "Critical priority — fix immediately",
});

// Add labels to an issue
await octokit.issues.addLabels({
  owner: "my-org",
  repo: "my-project",
  issue_number: 42,
  labels: ["reviewed", "ready-for-dev"],
});
```

## Milestones

```javascript
// Create a milestone
const { data: milestone } = await octokit.issues.createMilestone({
  owner: "my-org",
  repo: "my-project",
  title: "v2.0 Release",
  description: "All issues for the v2.0 release",
  due_on: "2026-06-01T00:00:00Z",
});

// Assign issue to milestone
await octokit.issues.update({
  owner: "my-org",
  repo: "my-project",
  issue_number: 42,
  milestone: milestone.number,
});
```

## Issue Templates

Define templates in `.github/ISSUE_TEMPLATE/` to standardize issue creation:

```yaml
# .github/ISSUE_TEMPLATE/bug_report.yml
name: Bug Report
description: Report a bug
labels: ["bug", "triage"]
body:
  - type: textarea
    id: description
    attributes:
      label: Describe the bug
    validations:
      required: true
  - type: textarea
    id: reproduction
    attributes:
      label: Steps to reproduce
    validations:
      required: true
```

## Environment Variables

| Variable | Purpose |
|----------|----------|
| `GITHUB_TOKEN` | Personal access token or installation token |
